            , <rs id="t17800510-46-deflabel246" type="occupation">spinster</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17800510-46-defend519 t17800510-46-deflabel246"></join>, were indicted for <rs id="t17800510-46-off247" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17800510-46-off247" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17800510-46-off247" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing ten yards of woollen cloth, value 15 s. three pair of linen gloves, value 2 s. two pair of laced ruffles, value 10 s. a pair of embroidered shoes, value 7 s. four yards of white edging, value 2 s. a pair of silk stockings, value 5 s. a muslin apron, value 5 s. a muslin handkerchief, value 2 s. three yards of silk ribbon, value 18 d. and a yard of black silk lace, value 1 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17800510-46-victim521" type="victimName">
                     Robert 
                     Jones
                  <interp inst="t17800510-46-victim521" type="surname" value="Jones"></interp>
